{"sha": "c03d658f7e39b642cd7305d1319eeb473048111f", "node_id": "MDY6Q29tbWl0NzI0NzEyOmMwM2Q2NThmN2UzOWI2NDJjZDczMDVkMTMxOWVlYjQ3MzA0ODExMWY=", "commit": {"author": {"name": "bors", "email": "bors@rust-lang.org", "date": "2014-04-22T15:41:32Z"}, "committer": {"name": "bors", "email": "bors@rust-lang.org", "date": "2014-04-22T15:41:32Z"}, "message": "auto merge of #13638 : alexcrichton/rust/fix-windows-tcp-timeout-bug, r=brson\n\nWhen a uv_tcp_t is closed in libuv, it will still invoke the pending connect_cb,\r\nand I thought that it would always call it with ECANCELED, but it turns out that\r\nsometimes we'll get a different error code instead. Handle this case by checking\r\nto see if the request's data is NULL and bail out if so (the timeout expired).", "tree": {"sha": "be75c87fa1365c364a6f47ff23198582967521b2", "url": "https://api.github.com/repos/rust-lang/rust/git/trees/be75c87fa1365c364a6f47ff23198582967521b2"}, "url": "https://api.github.com/repos/rust-lang/rust/git/commits/c03d658f7e39b642cd7305d1319eeb473048111f", "comment_count": 0, "verification": {"verified": false, "reason": "unsigned", "signature": null, "payload": null}}, "url": "https://api.github.com/repos/rust-lang/rust/commits/c03d658f7e39b642cd7305d1319eeb473048111f", "html_url": "https://github.com/rust-lang/rust/commit/c03d658f7e39b642cd7305d1319eeb473048111f", "comments_url": "https://api.github.com/repos/rust-lang/rust/commits/c03d658f7e39b642cd7305d1319eeb473048111f/comments", "author": {"login": "bors", "id": 3372342, "node_id": "MDQ6VXNlcjMzNzIzNDI=", "avatar_url": "https://avatars.githubusercontent.com/u/3372342?v=4", "gravatar_id": "", "url": "https://api.github.com/users/bors", "html_url": "https://github.com/bors", "followers_url": "https://api.github.com/users/bors/followers", "following_url": "https://api.github.com/users/bors/following{/other_user}", "gists_url": "https://api.github.com/users/bors/gists{/gist_id}", "starred_url": "https://api.github.com/users/bors/starred{/owner}{/re